  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DirectDownloadParameter
    This model class is the input parameter of direct download.
    DirectDownloadParameterBuilder
    This builder class creates the DirectDownloadParameter
    Downloader
    The Downloader class that handles the download functionality

    The Downloader creation requires a ConnectionConfig that defines generally where the download will be done.

    This model class is the input parameter of download.
    DownloadParameterBuilder

    DownloadResult

    The model class that defines the downloaded data
